text: Harish Kumar is an Indian athlete and a member of the Indian sepak takraw team. Kumar represented India in the 2018 Asian Games held in Jakarta and Palembang, Indonesia. Kumar was a part of the Indian sepak takraw team that secured the bronze medal at the Jakarta Palembang 2018 Asian Games. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Sepak takraw players at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Medalists at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games bronze medalists for India Category:Asian Games medalists in sepak takraw Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Indian sportspeople Category:Sepak takraw players
